				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Default dialogue for Gortash's mother, Sally Flymm, at Flymm Cobblers in the Lower City. Gortash tadpoled his parents, who sold him into slavery in his youth. They are aware of their state but cannot resist the tadpole's compulsion - which makes them appear as huge fans of their son."
